| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3847 — Recovery Inhibition (babuk2)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ecab7c2b-e75a-55ec-acd1-e4bee16316e4"
